# Robot program benchmarks

When comparing robot programs, validating player advice, or checking balance impact, use the rally benchmark harness:

```sh
cargo test -p robominer-domain benchmark_recommended_programs -- --nocapture
```

Harness: `robominer-domain/tests/program_recommendations.rs`

Edit the `programs`, `cases`, area helpers, and robot profile helpers in that file to try new source code, areas from `gameData.sql`, or part tiers. Scores are printed after tax; the default run averages 20 seeds (0..19) per program/area/robot combination.

This test is diagnostic output only — it is not part of the golden fixture suite and does not require a database.
